description:
Thanks to everyone for your support! =)

This project began with a very simple TNT Cannon idea. It was going to be just another one of my standard tutorial videos, but then I decided to try turn it into something cool for our 50000 subscriber special.

Spaz's Weapon of Mass Destruction:
- 1000 Single Shot, Mini Cannons
- 5000 TNT Total
- 200 Cannons Wide by 5 Cannons High
- Infinitely Expandable
- Hardcore Lag Inducing

This video took about 15 hours total to make, which includes cannon designing, world building, recording, editing, and of course... practicing.

Amazingly, I edited the whole thing using only VirtualDub and GoldWave.

Song: "Drifted", by Matt McFarland
Website: http://www.mattmcfarland.com/
